    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>258756</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_270_020_001</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>う〜……寒い……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Too...cold...!! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>259532</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_270_020_002</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>子どもは風の子！
がんばれ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Children are outdoor creatures! You can do it! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>260156</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_270_020_003</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>クルクルクル、クルール〜！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>KuruKuruKuru, Kururu! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>261668</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_270_020_005</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あの……
&lt;Rody&gt;さん……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Um, Miss Rody... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>262312</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_270_020_009</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>前にデリス・カーラーン
って言ってましたよね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You mentioned about Derris Kharlan once before... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>262612</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_270_020_010</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……言ってたっけ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...Oh, did I? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>262752</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_270_020_011</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ダオスが何か
持ち帰ろうとしてたって</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yes, the place Dhaos had to return to with one thing... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>263004</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_270_020_012</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>『大いなる実り』……だね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>The Mana Seed, yes... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>263144</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_270_020_013</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>デリス・カーラーン
ってダオスの故郷だっけ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Derris Kharlan is Dhaos' ho&lt;MEL&gt;and? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>263408</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_270_020_014</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そう……でも、今は
もうないかもね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Yes... But now it is no more... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>263660</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_270_020_015</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ない……？
なんで……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>No more...? Why? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>263800</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_270_020_016</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>戦争で滅亡寸前になった。
だから、彼はアセリアに
来たんだよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It was brought to the brink of destruction thanks to a war. 
That's why he needed to come here to this planet Aselia... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>263800</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_270_020_017</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>デリス・カーラーンの人々の命、
マナの源である『大いなる実り』
を故郷へ持ち帰るため</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Derris Kharlan people need Mana to live. For that purpose 
he had to bring back a Mana Seed to his home planet... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>263800</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_270_020_018</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、ダオスは
時空戦士に倒された</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But before he could finish his job, the Eternal Heroes 
struck him down... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>12</Id>
      <BubbleId>3</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>264180</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_270_020_019</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>え、じゃあ、
&lt;Cless&gt;さんたちのせいで
ダオスの故郷が……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So thanks to &lt;Cless&gt; and the others his people all... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>264500</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_270_020_020</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>間接的には
そういうことになるかな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Indirectly, at least. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>264820</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_270_020_021</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>…………</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>265140</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_270_020_022</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも！　&lt;Cless&gt;さんたちが、
悪いってわけじゃない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But &lt;Cless&gt; and the others aren't bad! </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>16</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>265460</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_270_020_023</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……だね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...I know. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>265460</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_270_020_024</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ダオスのやり方も
決して正しくは
なかったんだからさ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Dhaos' means of reaching his goal weren't justifiable. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>17</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>265900</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_270_020_025</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも、ダオスは
自分の故郷を救うために、
アセリアの人たちを襲ったんだ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But he only attacked Aselia and its people because he 
desperately needed to save Derris Kharlan... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>18</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>266220</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_270_020_026</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そ、世界樹を枯らす魔科学を
滅ぼして、世界樹になる
『大いなる実り』を手にするため</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's right. With the overuse of Magitechnology the Mana 
Tree, Yggdrasil, would wither away therefore not producing the 
Mana Seed he needed. </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>266220</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_270_020_027</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>でも……私にはやっぱり
どうしてもわかんない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But I never really understood...why he did things like he 
did... </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>266220</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>VSM_270_020_028</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>彼のような優しい人が、
どうしてあそこまで
非情になったのか……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>How could someone so kind and well-meaning do such 
heartless things...? </EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <BubbleId>3</BubbleId>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
</SceneText>
